name: Military Tent Pants - Enemy To Fashion x Anarke Jeans Co.
description:
Kicking off a series of projects with the guys over at Anarke jeans Co. with these pants constructed from vintage military tents. Each pant is unique in its coloring and retains original  stamps , seams, grommets and buttons from the original tents. Each pair is truly one of a kind and carries with it a piece of US history.

Each pair is handcrafted in North Carolina at the Anarke Jeans Co. by American hands one at a time.

A limited number of these will be available for pre-order on July 4th, Independence Day! Pants will ship 10 business days from the day you order as they will be custom made to your size.

Military Tent Pant $229.00 Shipped in Continental United States

- Made In The USA

- Cotton

- Button Fly

- Medium Rise

- Loose Fit

- Machine Wash

name: Enemy To Fashion - Jungle boot
description:
From the Enemy To Fashion Historical Reserve Collection...

This Limited Edition Boot Features a Vintage Military Issued Vietnam Era Upper and A Brand Spanking New Vibram Sole and Welt.

We Started by Hand Picking Each Military Boot for Its unique Character and Patina. Next We Deconstructed them and Married them to the Ever Popular and Comfy Vibram Sport Sole.


Each Pair Of Boots Is Unique.
Some Patches May Vary Slightly.
Each Pair Comes With White And Black Leather Laces.
Each Pair Is Signed And Numbered.

This limited edition Snapback hat features A button top, and plastic snap strap; tonal eyelets; green under brim; "Fuck Fashion" stitched front logo detail.

name: Enemy To Fashion - Vintage Quilt Duffle Backpack
description:

Each bag is a bit different in appearance than the one shown here due to the unique designs of each vintage quilt used.
